{"type": "article", "id": 20300, "title": "方糖音响", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-06T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145834DAVLXdN2HPbvI1wa.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是深圳米唐科技推出的可触控方糖（Sugr）迷你音箱，小巧可爱。触摸正上方，就可以打开开关，向左向右倾斜 45°时分别代表播放前一首和后一首，有种在手中把玩的亲切感。音响内有 4G 闪存，可存储 500 首歌，在有 WiFi 的情况下连上 Spotify 的 app，也能播放音乐。有白枫木和红樱桃木两种，单个售价 199 美元，<a href=\"http://www.sugrsugr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145832shGD9jIJ6vtbNK4L.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145832rEVYtMyZPHXouGDd.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145832PezKNZlFGjqtfrwB.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145833PIqyjXDSM0xUJtRl.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"409\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}